sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant Backend
    participant S3
    participant OpenAI
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>Frontend: Upload Resume PDF + JD
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/resumes/upload
    Backend->>S3: Store Original PDF
    S3-->>Backend: Return S3 Key
    Backend->>Backend: Parse PDF Text (PDFBox)
    Backend->>DB: Save Resume Entity
    Backend-->>Frontend: Return Resume ID

    User->>Frontend: Click "Optimize"
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/resumes/{id}/optimize
    Backend->>OpenAI: Send Original Text + JD + Rules
    Note right of OpenAI: Execute Strict<br/>Truthfulness<br/>Guard System
    OpenAI-->>Backend: Return Optimized JSON
    Backend->>Backend: Calculate Integrity Scores
    alt Integrity Score < 95%
        Backend-->>Frontend: Reject Optimization
    else Integrity Score >= 95%
        Backend->>DB: Update Resume Entity
        Backend-->>Frontend: Return Optimized Content
    end
